<subSubSection pageId="137" pageNumber="708" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="137.[824,1411,2715,3138]" pageId="137" pageNumber="708">
Formerly considered a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName class="Mammalia" family="Bovidae" genus="Sylvicapra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="137" pageNumber="708" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="grimmia">S. grimmia</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Gray" baseAuthorityYear="1842" box="[955,1101,2838,2863]" class="Mammalia" family="Bovidae" genus="Cephalophora" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="137" pageNumber="708" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="coronata">S. coronata</taxonomicName>
is herein considered to be a separate species. The Bush Duiker subspecies 
<taxonomicName box="[986,1287,2908,2941]" class="Mammalia" family="Bovidae" genus="Sylvicapra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="137" pageNumber="708" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="grimmia" subSpecies="campbelliae">S. grimmia campbelliae</taxonomicName>
and the 
<collectingRegion box="[826,901,2951,2980]" country="Burkina Faso" name="Sahel" pageId="137" pageNumber="708">Sahel</collectingRegion>
Duiker (
<taxonomicName box="[1037,1180,2951,2980]" class="Mammalia" family="Bovidae" genus="Sylvicapra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="137" pageNumber="708" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pallidior">S. pallidior</taxonomicName>
) are sometimes attributed to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Gray" baseAuthorityYear="1842" box="[1025,1172,2986,3019]" class="Mammalia" family="Bovidae" genus="Sylvicapra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="137" pageNumber="708" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="coronata">S. coronata</taxonomicName>
in literature reports, although this species, strictly speaking, is restricted to coastal West Africa. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[210,1035,3153,3178]" pageId="137" pageNumber="708" type="distribution">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6512815" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6512815" box="[210,1035,3153,3178]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6512815/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="137" pageNumber="708" targetBox="[202,795,835,1249]" targetPageId="137">
